   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can enable email notifications from the Email Recipients page. When enabled, email notifications are sent to each registered recipient any time a sync fails to execute or has errors. Email notifications are sent for both real-time and scheduled sync. When a sync fails due to an error, an email is sent with error details. A maximum of five email Ids can be added. Email notifications are disabled by default. You can also customize the email template to be used for notification.</p>
